1. controlled form are essial from react

2. uncontrolled form are essial from react

3. for fromhanding  and validation we have some 3rd party modules or library
  --> formik and yup
  https://formik.org/
  
  Formik is a small library that helps you with the 3 most annoying parts: 
    -> Getting values in and out of form state
    -> Validation and error messages
    -> Handling form submission
    -> useFormik() is a custom React hook that will return all Formik state and helpers directly
        npm i formik --save
       schema Validation with Yup
        npm i yup --save

localdata storage : 
  It is a useful feature that allow developers to store and retrieve data locally within a user's web browser. It allow us to preserve user prefernces , session information or any other data that has to be saved between page refreshes or even browser session.
  -> Cookies : store small amount of data upto 4k
  -> Localstorage : It is permanent and store upto 5mb of data
         -> How we set data
        localStorage.setItem(key, value)

        -> How we get data
           localStorage.getItem(key)
        
        -> How we remove data
           localStorage.removeItem(key)
  -> Sessionstorage : It is temporary and store upto 5mb of data
         -> How we set data
        Sessionstorage.setItem(key, value)

        -> How we get data
           Sessionstorage.getItem(key)
        
        -> How we remove data
           Sessionstorage.removeItem(key)

